[SHORT DESC]
Burns the target.

[LONG DESC]
<h2>Description</h2>
<p>Deals damage and has a 100% chance to burn the target.</p>

<h2>Competitive Use</h2>
<p>Inferno has little competitive use. Despite its 100% chance to burn the target, its accuracy is horribly low, making the move unreliable.</p>

<h2>Related Moves</h2>
<p><a href="/bw/moves/flamethrower">Flamethrower</a> is a slightly weaker, but much more accurate alternative that has a 10% chance to burn the target.</p>
<p><a href="/bw/moves/fire_blast">Fire Blast</a> is a much stronger alternative that has a 10% chance to burn the target.</p>
<p><a href="/bw/moves/lava_plume">Lava Plume</a> is a slightly weaker, but much more accurate alternative that has a 30% chance to burn the target.</p>